/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-PBy92bBuBMMs53v9tc9E0A">Hồ Xuân Hương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Ki%E1%BB%87u/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-h%E1%BA%A1nh-Vi-T%E1%BB%B1-L%E1%BA%ADp-S%C6%A1n-trang-th%E1%BB%8B-y%E1%BA%BFn-%E1%BB%A9ng-ch%E1%BA%BF/poem-9z7tlaJ2L4laWoPZ6D-CgA">Phụng hoạ hạnh Vi Tự Lập “Sơn trang thị yến” ứng chế - 奉和幸韋嗣立山莊侍宴應制</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Ki%E1%BB%87u/author-yGOsh2Zg2gUgZ09A-P6xFA">Lý Kiệu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Th%E1%BB%A9/Qu%C3%A1i-th%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-o2Zfhp_BVQj8Qv6j587dUQ">Quái thạch - 怪石</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Th%E1%BB%A9/author-ZHWz4JBODdUpO8rA9B3TfQ">Hoàng Thứ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Quan-L%C3%BD-C%E1%BB%91-Th%E1%BB%89nh-t%C6%B0-m%C3%A3-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-s%C6%A1n-thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-CI17vANvnGuZPBg85EtKIg">Quan Lý Cố Thỉnh tư mã đệ sơn thuỷ đồ kỳ 3 - 觀李固請司馬弟山水圖其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-Khi%C3%AAm/Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-s%C6%A1n/poem-j2O-KPMlWWw2tPMgsN9MKw">Trọng sơn - 仲山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-Khi%C3%AAm/author-0IgWRHCvEyX64lV-HaskRg">Đường Ngạn Khiêm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
